projects.name: Smart Parking System
projects.description: Successfully integrated YOLO-v8 model, achieving a detection accuracy of over 90%. Optimized model parameters to reduce inference time by 30%, ensuring real-time processing even in challenging conditions. Developed algorithms to accurately determine parking space occupancy status with a precision rate of 90%. Engineered a robust notification system to inform users instantly about available parking spots, resulting in a 40% increase in user engagement and parking space utilization.

projects.name: A-eye Vision
projects.description: Attained an object detection accuracy exceeding 90% in real-world conditions, bolstering user confidence in the systems reliability. Deployed a sophisticated voice prompt system, enhancing accessibility and comprehension for visually impaired users. Significantly reduced processing time to less than 100 milliseconds per frame, ensuring near-real-time performance in various scenarios.

experiences.description: Gained extensive hands-on experience in Python through mentor-led training sessions and practical case studies, leading to the development of real-world projects. Executed projects that integrated SQL databases with Python applications, demonstrating strong skills in database management and programming.
